dataIdInfo.idPurp: This layer provides an index map that can be used to locate individual scanned map sheets.
dataIdInfo.idAbs: • This polygon shapefile is an index to 1:25,000 scale maps of Vladivostok Region (Russia), titled 'Urajio kinbō niman-gosenbun no ichi zu -- 浦潮近傍二万五千分一圖/Urajio kinbō niman-gosenbun no ichi zu.’ To create this index, footprints were generated using the fishnet tool, and metadata were supplied for the digitized paper maps by Stanford University Libraries. After the footprints were created, the shapefile was trimmed and labeled according to the sources.
dataIdInfo.idCredit: Stanford University Libraries, Stanford Geospatial Center
